@jakovanrensburg 

In my opinion, the search should be under the Credit heading and be called "Maintenance Order Registry".

There should also be a tick box forcing the user to accept that "This search is only to be used for the prescribed purpose of an affordability assessment during the application for credit."

The user must also accept the terms and conditions and that they have acquired the consumer's consent.

@shaunviljoen @gillianoberholzer @cobuspienaar
